Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}are waiting for the moment\N{\c&He1e1e1&}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The words we exchange\N{\c&He1e1e1&}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}and a chance meeting\N{\c&He1e1e1&}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}People, no matter who they are,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}As we leave behind a living\N{\c&He1e1e1&}testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}the Galaxy Railways on which\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we travel continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A gun that doesn't work is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}worse than a security blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Understood. I will carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But I will not use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The time when you will have to use it\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will come, in order for you to survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}That is the law of the universe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The stations that the Galaxy Railways\N{\c&He1e1e1&}stop at are not only located on planets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}There are railway junctions that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}float out in the middle of the cosmos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}People switch trains here, and decide\N{\c&He1e1e1&}which paths they will take to continue on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Thus they become turning points.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A prison train is arriving\N{\c&He1e1e1&}at the special trains platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Turning Point"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's right.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}A Sirius Platoon mixer party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:02:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--Cool!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I recently won a somewhat\N{\c&He1e1e1&}considerable bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Some high-class wine will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}be arriving this weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and I'll be furnishing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're coming, right? Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Bulge,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you'll be coming too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The captain can't very well miss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This will be nice for a change. I may\N{\c&He1e1e1&}not be able to cover the whole thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but I'll pick up the tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, that's what I like about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Aw, and here I was going\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to drink on the sly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That means the funding will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll add some caviar and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}mozzarella cheese to snack on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, you'll be coming too,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of course, right? ...Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She said she was going to the medical car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I guess she's standing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}us up again this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki has never been one to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}show up for off-duty gatherings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm starting to wonder if\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0} dislikes all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, now, don't take that too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Find an escape pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Four prisoners appear to have escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}from the prison train\N{\c&He1e1e1&}stopped at Junction Alpha 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Report on the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Currently, they are inside the junction,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}fleeing toward Passageway A25.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Emergency alert status.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Lock down Junction Alpha 32 at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Uh, that's not why I'm here.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is it about work? Or maybe\N{\c&He1e1e1&}your personal relationships?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please do not worry,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I will keep your secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You came for counseling, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are there currently any SDF trains\N{\c&He1e1e1&}en route to that area?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} is on her way home\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from Ariadne Junction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, do not laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Since there is nothing wrong\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with your physical condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I thought that surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm sorry. It's just that there\N{\c&He1e1e1&}was something I was concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All of that party talk earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ah. Please be sure to enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Um, is it somehow uncomfortable\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for you to be around us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well then, come! You've never\N{\c&He1e1e1&}been to a party before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It will be fun, having\N{\c&He1e1e1&}all of your friends around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am of the understanding\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that "friend" is a word
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}used to describe relationships\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that humans have with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am just a medical sexaroid,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}so it does not apply to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well, that's just--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is that terrible smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Acetic acid, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is the smell coming from this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please do not touch his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Antilian blood has a unique composition,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and when it comes in contact with\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the air, it starts to oxidize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It happens more rapidly\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the longer it is exposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and by and by, it becomes a strong acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've applied a neutralizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to go over our strategy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There are four prisoners who have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We believe that one of them has\N{\c&He1e1e1&}stolen an SDF member's gun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and is carrying it with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Two of the prisoners are co-conspirators.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}The other two acted on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Since they are not acquaintances,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we believe that they have split up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and are escaping in\N{\c&He1e1e1&}three different directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the matter, Liza?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I- I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We don't have time to dawdle around.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All of them are criminals who are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in prison for committing murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no telling what they will do.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Acting alone would be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll search for them in teams of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, this time, you'll have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to join us in the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David and Louis, Manabu and Yuki,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}me and Bruce is how we'll conduct this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--Acknowledged!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--Acknowledged!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--Acknowledged!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You might have to use your gun\N{\c&He1e1e1&}on this case. Be ready for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Of course, I mean the gun that works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He went through there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's nothing unusual in Block A.25.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Moving to Block B.18.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy that. There's no telling where\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the enemy will be coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've found one! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've come across one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He's fleeing through the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}industrial corridor towards Block F.9.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We can't catch up to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter how strong your legs may be,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I doubt you can get down that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've got one of them captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}In the dark, I'm home free!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The dark may be your specialty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but you can't make a clean escape\N{\c&He1e1e1&}if you don't know your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've captured another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's two of them left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Those are oxidized skin cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's some over here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The trail of blood continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It looks like the criminals are fleeing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}after having had Antilian blood\N{\c&He1e1e1&}spilled on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If we don't hurry,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}it will be too late for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Liza! Get up! We're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The trail of blood has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Watch out! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They could be right nearby.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}They've got a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Looks like they arrested\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the bleeding and got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But they won't stop the hemorrhaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They'll be leaving another\N{\c&He1e1e1&}trail of blood before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're trying to conceal the trail\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of blood in this darkness, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There isn't any time.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}We have to find them quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stop! They could be hiding in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn! There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's no use trying to escape! Don't add\N{\c&He1e1e1&}anything else to your list of crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even if we do nothing,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}they'll still send us to Alcarz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter what we do now, it doesn't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}get any more serious than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You'll be surrounded in mere moments!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no way you can escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We found the two of them, and made contact.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}They're in Block C.48.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll head there immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}At this rate, her whole body\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will be eaten away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If I don't tend to her soon,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}her life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Listen to me! If you keep this up,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}she's going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Die...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Throw down your weapon and surrender!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}There's still time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You expect us to fall for that trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Believe me! She's come in\N{\c&He1e1e1&}contact with Antilian blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You get it, right? Now, hurry\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and lay down your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no time to spare!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Throw down your gun to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, we're coming\N{\c&He1e1e1&}over there now to treat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it, I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Liza, we're getting out of here, now.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leo, help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no time left. I'm going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki! You can't! It's too dangerous for\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you to go over to the criminals alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even if they attack me,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I will not feel pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If I am destroyed, you will be provided\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with a replacement sexaroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I won't make any trouble for the platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You dimwit! What do you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}take yourself for!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am the medical sexaroid\N{\c&He1e1e1&}assigned to the Sirius Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No! You're our friend!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can't just watch a friend of mine\N{\c&He1e1e1&}walk into danger like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Friend...? I am a medical sexaroid.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I was built to help people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}When I see someone in pain\N{\c&He1e1e1&}before my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I cannot just stand by and watch.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, let me go treat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Help me... I don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's a medical expert on her way over!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}That's all right, isn't it? Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Very well. Send the woman over alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's okay now. I will treat you at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stand up nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to treat her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll give you plenty of time later.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki! Let Yuki go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Lose the gun, and get\N{\c&He1e1e1&}an escape pod ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't do anything foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Like I said, it can't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}get any worse for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you don't treat her right away,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}she's going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you going to drop it or not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The other one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please! I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leo, let that woman go!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry! She has to tend to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Help me, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, Leo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How could you do that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She would have died anyway\N{\c&He1e1e1&}if I'd left her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's better for her that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I put her down easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She would have lived\N{\c&He1e1e1&}if she had been treated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"If" is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You... planned this from the start...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And what if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}W- why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now, get rid of the gun and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}get your hands up! Or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You mustn't, Yuuki-{\i1}san{\i0}!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Do not concern yourself about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, carry out your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Would you hurry it up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}san{\i0}! Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right... now then, you're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you okay, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David, lend me a hand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Can you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Any regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's go, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Once again, you've carved out\N{\c&He1e1e1&}your own destiny... for yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, you nervous about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're not worried that this is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}going to be a stag party, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're looking absolutely adorable today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Eh? I guess clothes\N{\c&He1e1e1&}really do make the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Geez, how rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And yet, even as you're saying so,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you're feasting your eyes on Louis-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}N- not at all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm sorry I'm late,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}but I had to file a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm resuming my duties as of today.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I hope you'll accept my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right! That makes\N{\c&He1e1e1&}tonight's party a mixer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}as well as a celebration\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of Yuki's recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}When we hold on to stubborn beliefs,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}it sometimes creates\N{\c&He1e1e1&}barriers for ourselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}However, once we come in contact{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}with what lies on the other side of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}those barriers, that's when we realize...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The barriers were only\N{\c&He1e1e1&}there within ourselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}How many nights have I\N{\c&He1e1e1&}spent alone since then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:22:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Constantly having dreams of the hope\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that you are, as I lightly sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The smiles and tears that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you gave to me and me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}come to mind every time\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I get disheartened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}and I set forth again toward the morrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The joyful light of the galaxy beckons me{\i0}
